Package: horseshoeocc
Type: Package
Title: Package for Fitting and Summarizing Occupancy Models Using the Regularized Horseshoe Prior
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Meaghan", "Winder", email = "mwinder@middlebury.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description:  This package allows for the fitting and summarizing of the
    occupancy model described by \href{https://doi.org/10.1890/0012-9658(2002)083[2248:ESORWD]2.0.CO;2}{MacKenzie et al. (2002)}
    using the regularized horseshoe prior described by
    \href{https://doi.org/10.1214/17-EJS1337SI}{Piironen and Vehtari (2017)} with
    a prior on \eqn{p0}. 
License: None.
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
Imports: 
    coda,
    dplyr,
    HDInterval,
    magrittr,
    R2jags,
    stringr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
